text: "High on Life" is a 2018 song by Dutch DJ Martin Garrix and featuring Swedish songwriter and vocalist Bonn. It went to number 1 in Belgium, number 11 in New Zealand, number 19 in the Netherlands, number 29 in Sweden, number 31 in Hungary, number 35 in Slovakia, number 37 in the Czech Republic, number 45 in Switzerland and number 52 in Austria. == References == Category:2018 songs Category:Martin Garrix songs
title: High on Life (song)
